+# PR 214 Remediation Report
+
+## Thread Classification
+
+- `T-214-01`: actionable
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete outdated-hunk suggestion
+- `T-214-04`: actionable
+- `T-214-05`: actionable
+
+## Code Changes
+
+- `src/policy/approval_router.py`: normalize `approval_state` before calling
+  `build_preview_payload(...)` so `manual_review` becomes
+  `human_review_required` for both live and fallback preview responses.
+- `src/policy/preview.py`: keep `approval_state` and
+  `requires_human_review` in the fallback `preview_unavailable` payload.
+- `tests/test_preview.py`: add regression coverage for
+  `build_policy_preview(..., preview_enabled=False, approval_state="manual_review", ...)`
+  and assert the fallback payload preserves
